             was indicted for <rs id="t18310217-100-off601" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310217-100-off601" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310217-100-off601" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18310217-100-victim1046" type="victimName">
                           Elizabeth 
                           Westwood
                        <interp inst="t18310217-100-victim1046" type="surname" value="Westwood"></interp>
